  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to escape from a mysterious village shrouded in thick fog. At every turn you'll have to explore ominous locations, solve puzzles and find key clues to move forward. But be careful - there are zombies in the village, ready to attack at any second. Your goal is to find a way to escape as well as stay alive in this terrifying location.</p>",
